a:17:{s:4:"name";s:7:"Haridra";s:11:"small_descr";s:75:"Haridra  is a well-known herb that helps in combating allergy effectively. ";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:69:"Haridra ist ein berühmtes Kraut, das der Allergie-Bekämpfung dient.";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:72:"Haridra est une herbe bien connue qui traite efficacement les allergies.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:87:"Haridra es una hierba bien conocida que ayuda a luchar efectivamente contra la alergia.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:76:"Haridra è un'erba ben nota che aiuta a combattere con efficacia l'allergia.";s:10:"full_descr";s:989:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p>Haridra has many medicinal properties - it is a well-known herb that helps in combating allergy effectively.&nbsp;It has anti-inflammatory and anti-allergic activity. It helps in faster wound healing and has blood-purifying properties. It also acts as a carminative, stomachic, appetizer and tonic.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS</strong></p><p>Take exactly as recommended by your Health Provider.</p><p>If you miss a dose of Haridra and you are using it regularly, use it as soon as possible. Do not use 2 doses at once.</p><p><strong>DOSAGE</strong></p><p>Take 1 capsule twice a day after meals.</p><p><strong>STORAGE</strong></p><p>Store at the room temperature away from moisture and sunlight. Keep out of reach of children.</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p>There are no know precautions for using Haridra.</p><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>Haridra isn't known to have any side effects if taken as per the prescribed dosage.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:7:"50.1448";s:9:"pack_name";s:6:"bottle";s:4:"type";s:4:"caps";s:7:"analogs";N;s:18:"active_ingredients";N;s:8:"packings";a:1:{i:60;a:1:{i:5409;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5409";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:6:"dosage";d:60;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"50.1448";s:4:"name";s:7:"Haridra";}}}}